Package: mdufa
Title: Structured Data on FDA's Medical Device User Fee Program Performance 
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Brendan",
           family = "O'Leary",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "brendan@boleary.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8753-917X"))
Description: |
    This package includes structured data from the FDA's quarterly Medical 
    Device User Fee Ammendments (MDUFA) programs, which are published as PDFs 
    on fda.gov. The package includes functions to scrape those PDFs to extract 
    the data and includes the most recent dataset as of publication. 
